'''釙化鈉'''是一種[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，由2種金屬化合而成:[[釙|釙]]和[[鈉|鈉]]，化學式為:Na<sub>2</sub>Po。'''釙化鈉'''的晶體結構為反[[螢石|螢石]]型結構<ref name="G&E">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw1st|page=899}}</ref><ref name="AEC-chem">{{citation | last = Moyer | first = Harvey V. | contribution = Chemical Properties of Polonium | pages = 33–96 | title = Polonium | url = http://www.osti.gov/bridge/servlets/purl/4367751-nEJIbm/ | editor-last = Moyer | editor-first = Harvey V. | id = TID-5221 | doi = 10.2172/4367751 | year = 1956 | location = Oak Ridge, Tenn. | publisher = United States Atomic Energy Commission | accessdate = 2011-08-11 | archive-date = 2019-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190701105103/https://www.osti.gov/biblio/4367751 | dead-url = no }}.</ref>，和其他[[氧族元素|氧族元素]][[化合物|化]][[鹼金屬|鹼金屬]]類似([[氧化鈉|氧化鈉]]、[[硫化鈉|硫化鈉]]、[[硒化鈉|硒化鈉]]、[[碲化鈉|碲化鈉]])。

==制备==
要制備釙化鈉，可以使[[釙化氫|釙化氫]]水溶液（氫釙酸）和[[鈉|鈉]]發生[[酸鹼中和|酸鹼中和]]而產生。<ref name="G&E"/><ref name="AEC-chem"/>
:H<sub>2</sub>Po + 2 Na → Na<sub>2</sub>Po + H<sub>2</sub>
这个反应的阻碍是钋化氢的不稳定性。

钋和钠在300–400 °C下直接反应，也可以得到钋化钠。<ref name="Bagnall"/>

